org.perfidix.element

Class NoMethodArrangement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfidix.element.AbstractMethodArrangement
      • org.perfidix.element.NoMethodArrangement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<BenchmarkElement>

    public final class NoMethodArrangement
extends AbstractMethodArrangement
    This class does no arrangement for methods. That means that the order of the input is given back as the order of the output as well.
    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
